nodes.text: Norath Kev was a Duros male Resistance spy who operated during the war between the Resistance and the First Order. Some time after the Hosnian Cataclysm, he was captured by Ax Tagrin, but then later escaped together with Kazuda Xiono. Kev later joined Jade Squadron, flying a T-70 X-wing starfighter.
Norath Kev first appeared in "The Missing Agent", an episode of second season of Star Wars Resistance where he was voiced by Daveed Diggs. His design was based off pre-production work for the series.
